sub_title: I am a dedicated teacher of foreign languages, trying to implement and discover new and successful ways of teaching foreign languages.
summary:
My passion for languages and teaching gave me the opportunity to discover new ways of teaching foreign languages. Thanks to the experience gained as a German and English teacher, I have the ability to implement different kinds of teaching methods in my lessons and motivate the students to learn a new language. 
My idea is to go beyond the grammar lessons, letting the students understand the culture and giving them the experience of a "full immersion" using CLT (communicative language teaching) as the main tool. 
My social skills make it possible to create a safe and fun learning environment for the student, where every mistake is not seen as a disappointment, rather as a reminder to keep trying.
